					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="100 Brilliant Companies to Watch in 2016" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160518161614-brilliant-100.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
